Package edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations

Contains annotation interfaces for class, method, operator, built-in function, and &-keyword metadata.

See: Description

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Over.OverTypes
    Argument types of operators and functions: over iterators, properties (also called atoms), variables, or values.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    MField
    Annotation interface for class fields.
    MFunction
    Annotation interface for built-in functions.
    MKeyword
    Annotation interface for &-keywords.
    MLocal
    Annotation interface for method local variables.
    MLocals
    Container for local variable annotations.
    MMethod
    Annotation interface for methods.
    MMethodRef
    Annotation interface for method reference.
    MOperator
    Annotation interface for operators.
    MParameter
    Annotation interface for method parameters.
    MParameters
    Container for parameter annotations.
    MSource
    Annotation interface for source code.
    Over
    Annotation interface for argument type of functions and operators.

Package edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations Description

Contains annotation interfaces for class, method, operator, built-in function, and &-keyword metadata.
